en you killed verrina.  for those of us whos group will be KOS to go in adn kll her, whats the easy way to get in and puller her. i was thinking  maybe  a DE cleric with DB that could   pull just her. so that all those other NPCs dont add.    what have you learned about  how MR this shissar is?  drozlin? what tactics worked for you guys.  this will be my guilds first  epic chanter.  no one is there with the knowledge of doing these battles. so anything you can tell me that will mean less of  my friends   and guidlies  dead on these mobs would be   humbly appreciated. <br>
