<br>
Verina - bring 2 groups 50+ to zone in of neriak 3rd gate.  Kill the wandering guards (about lvl 35 to 40).  Have a rouge with DE illusion pull her from cleric guild to the groups.  She is not on any faction and no one will come with her.  She is a lvl 55 cleric so watch for CH.<br>
<br>
Cazel - He is a random spawn so good luck with him.  Have a guildie camp out looking for him.  The spoon is NOT no drop, so anyone in your guild can kill him and loot the spoon for you.  Often he is killed by necros who will give the spoon away so don't despair.<br>
<br>
The Sissar is very MR and is triggered by killing CT.  This is normally the last piece of the epic you will get because many lvl 60 chanters are still waaiting for her to spawn.  If you do not have a guild that can solo PoF, you are in for a long wait on this part.<br>
<br>
Drozlin - He is a hard one.  The hardest part is getting to him without loosing half your group.  He is MR, but you can land spells on him.  There is really no safe way to kill him.  Bring enough ppl to overkill is about all I can say.  You have to go deep within Cabalis to get to him, but through the sewers is the safest way (less time avoiding guards).  Kill him fast is the only thing I have left to say.<br>
<br>
Hope this clears some things up.  I have not gotten most of these pieces myself, but I have helped.  Good luck.<br>
<br>
